{"tid":513843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉辱國旗　古思堯遭預約拘捕","createTime":"2017-12-30T03:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T11:58:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"de4b658e22ae6adba59b0f19a27ec4aeacec0a62","tid":513843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20259735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259735&d=HTkgQh88nNAuM2dD5rtKtpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fa9d8b93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259735&h=70e0011d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20259735</a><br />\n<br />\n涉辱國旗　古思堯遭預約拘捕<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171230/large/a0304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171230%2Flarge%2Fa0304a.gif&h=6a8b468b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古思堯（中）指不害怕入獄，會繼續抗爭。<br />\n社民連提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾因焚燒區旗示威被判入獄的社民連成員古思堯，涉嫌於今年兩次遊行中，分別塗污、毀壞及倒置國旗，昨再被落案控告兩項「侮辱國旗」罪，下月於東區裁判法院提堂，獲准以200元保釋。古思堯料百分之二百要再坐監，但會繼續對抗中共法西斯極權專政，無畏也無懼，「坐完出來再抗爭」。<br />\n<br />\n稱不怕入獄　下月5日提堂<br />\n<br />\n古思堯於昨日早上前往灣仔警察總部接受預約拘捕，約10名社民連成員到場聲援，高喊口號，批評政治檢控可恥，要求廢除國旗法。古思堯表示，不滿中共政權專制極權，所以以侮辱區旗及國旗對抗，但強調屬其個人選擇的示威方式，並不鼓勵其他人仿效，因為要承擔坐監風險。他預料自己會再次入獄，但明言屢敗屢戰，「坐完出來再抗爭，抗爭完再進去坐，一點也不會畏懼」。<br />\n<br />\n古思堯涉嫌於今年7月15日悼念劉曉波燭光遊行中，踐踏及焚燒國旗；其後在10月1日反威權遊行中，他在一個寫上「為共和國送終」的時鐘示威道具上，張貼倒置國旗，以諷刺中共不尊重人權，劉霞不得自由，遭警方沿途監視，並警告涉違法。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，昨日拘捕一名71歲古姓男子，涉嫌於上述日子的公眾活動上，分別塗污、毀壞國旗及倒置國旗，已落案控告兩項「侮辱國旗」罪，案件將於下月5日在東區裁判法院提堂，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款港幣5萬元及監禁3年。<br />\n<br />\n社民連梁國雄批評，現行法例不容許以區旗及國旗作意見表達，限制言論自由，「就係呢條例恐怖之處」，促廢法還民。古思堯於前年7.1涉焚燒區旗示威，被控侮辱區旗罪，去年3月裁定罪成，即時入獄6星期。當時古思堯不作求情，更希望法庭不要對他仁慈，表明願意承擔後果，入獄更是抗爭一部份。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"3f64120150b54db127f40b33a48bd91b31a908ac","tid":513843,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"喂喂"},{"pid":"80f1be7631fc6a9759cdb439ca6fbff8cfeb2d76","tid":513843,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"喂喂喂"},{"pid":"caebfdceda5796f3174980e3c195cc374d9d6cea","tid":513843,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b680be63d1545bb8a03edf215f49f8e654b5678","tid":513843,"uid":23993,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:39:01.000Z","msg":"喂喂 喂 你企開啲啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"7fcba1d25d3a1524aa5c89fac609c9f91cbfbd44","tid":513843,"uid":11890,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/114006_0daeb1e5594ffb9f230679dce3a35117.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F114006_0daeb1e5594ffb9f230679dce3a35117.jpeg&h=fdc76500&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/30/114008_e15b8a1e996b43e83003895c4a84fec6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F30%2F114008_e15b8a1e996b43e83003895c4a84fec6.jpeg&h=87dfc490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾時拉晒呢啲侮辱國旗嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b13f8f51bd193c5493d523bdb7c52fa6492525","tid":513843,"uid":104213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b7ab8e03c4784ba35493d